<section class="section section--42-60-0-72">
	<h2>Conversion Strategy</h2>
	<p class="ec-conversion-strategy-text">One of the primary business goals was reducing friction between product discovery and purchase completion. Rather than focusing only on interface design, I analyzed the entire shopping journey to identify points where users could hesitate or abandon the purchase process. <br><br>These improvements helped create a smoother transition from product exploration to checkout while supporting the business goal of increasing purchase completion.</p>
	<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-wrapper">
		<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-items">
			<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item">
				<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item__number">01</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Improved Product Visibility</h3>
					<p>Structured product information and imagery to help users evaluate products faster.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item">
				<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item__number">02</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Reduced Decision Fatigue</h3>
					<p>Presented information in digestible sections and prioritized the most relevant content.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item">
				<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item__number">03</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Clear Purchase Actions</h3>
					<p>Created a consistent call-to-action hierarchy across product and checkout pages.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item">
				<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-item__number">04</div>
				<div>
					<h3>Checkout Experience</h3>
					<p>Ensured users always understood pricing, order details, and next steps throughout the purchase flow.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ec-conversion-strategy-image">
			<img src="/assets/img/e-commerce/comments.png" alt="Checkout conversion comments and design notes">
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
